  <source>St. Antonius Hospital</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will investigate the pharmacokinetics of acetaminophen in morbidly obese patients
      versus normal weight patients. Specifically the different metabolic pathways of acetaminophen
      in morbidly obese adults will be investigated; glucuronidation, sulphation and CYP2E1
      (cytochrome P450 2E1) oxidation
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
